rows.label: tlk41700121_06_msg0001
rows.name:
About ten years ago, I think it was? The
lord of a city belonging to one of Gula's
seven main tribes was replaced.

rows.label: tlk41700121_06_msg0002
rows.name:
That lord had two daughters,
but one of them was sickly.

rows.label: tlk41700121_06_msg0003
rows.name:
He was spending a huge amount
of money on her treatment.

rows.label: tlk41700121_06_msg0005
rows.name:
I can understand wanting to
do whatever it takes for your
precious daughter, but...

rows.label: tlk41700121_06_msg0006
rows.name:
A lord shouldn't do
something like that...

rows.label: tlk41700121_06_msg0007
rows.name:
Not that a consul like Morph
was any better, but I hope we
get a good one next time.
